{
  "stem": "14091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was built to-- for the future for my two sisters, when-- if they will get married, that they would live there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember also my mother used to send me every Friday with little packages to bring to people who couldn't afford.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She would bake challah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She would milk the cows and send milk, cheese, and challah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I used to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Also, she would ask my sister Celia-- she was older than I-- and she went with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had so many friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The family was large because there were uncles and aunts and cousins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was an interwoven family, so I never, never felt that I was missing anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was-- [SIGHS] it was so beautiful, although we didn't have any bathroom in the house or running water.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had an outhouse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And water was brought in in by-- in barrels, and it was standing in the entrance in a big wooden barrel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Later on, my father, they could afford and we had a well in the back, which it was done with the bringing out the water in, in buckets.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Electricity came also later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember before we had lamps in every room in the evening, my sisters would go and put up the gasoline in each lamp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this how we had light.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I remember it was such a relation that electricity was brought in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I remember hanging that electric bulb in each room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This was very exciting, because after that, they start also bringing the movies that I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And life became much more exciting because of the electricity.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My father loved to read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And his time, the time that he had left over from working and-- he used to read a lot.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
